om%2Fundermanaging-basses-as-toxic-as-micromanagers-expert-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Rs%201%20Lakh%20Loan%20With%20Maximum%205%25%20Interest%20Under%20Vishwakarma%20Scheme%5C%22%3A%20Centre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Cabinet%20Committee%20on%20Economic%20Affairs%20(CCEA)%20chaired%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20approved%20a%20new%20central%20sector%20scheme%20-%20%26quot%3BPM%20Vishwakarma%26quot%3B.%20The%20scheme%2C%20which%20was%20announced%20by%20the%20PM%20in%20his%20Independence%20Day%20speech%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20will%20benefit%2030%20lakh%20craftsmen%20and%20their%20families%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%2C%20with%20a%20financial%20outlay%20of%20Rs%2013%2C000%20crore%20for%20a%20period%20of%20five%20years%20until%202028%2C%20will%20cover%2018%20traditional%20trades%20in%20the%20first%20instance%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20PM%20Vishwakarma%20scheme%2C%20artisans%20and%20craftspeople%20will%20be%20provided%20recognition%20through%20PM%20Vishwakarma%20certificates%2C%20ID%20cards%2C%20credit%20support%20upto%20Rs%201%20lakh%20(in%20the%20first%20tranche)%20and%20Rs%202%20lakh%20(in%20the%20second%20tranche)%20with%20a%20concessional%20interest%20rate%20of%205%25.%20The%20scheme%20will%20further%20provide%20skill%20upgradation%2C%20toolkit%20incentive%2C%20incentive%20for%20digital%20transactions%2C%20and%20marketing%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Centre%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20covered%20in%20the%20first%20instance%20under%20%26quot%3BPM%20Vishwakarma%26quot%3B%20include%20carpenters%2C%20boat%20makers%2C%20blacksmiths%2C%20locksmiths%2C%20goldsmiths%2C%20potters%2C%20sculptors%2C%20cobblers%2C%20and%20masons%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20CCEA%20also%20greenlit%20the%20%26quot%3BPM-eBus%20Sewa%26quot%3B%20under%20whic