FTSMC-founder-Morris-Chang-backs-U.S.-on-China-chip-curbs%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BHis%20wife%20will%20ask%3A%20'What's%20the%20matter%3F'%20He%20would%20say%3A%20'I%20need%20to%20go%20to%20the%20factory.'%20The%20wife%20will%20go%20back%20to%20sleep%20without%20saying%20another%20word.%20This%20is%20the%20work%20culture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETSMC%20employees%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F02%2F22%2Ftechnology%2Ftsmc-arizona-factory-tensions.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20in%20February%20they%20were%20skeptical%20that%20American%20workers%20would%20be%20willing%20to%20make%20the%20same%20sacrifices%20as%20workers%20in%20Taiwan%20and%20said%20Taiwanese%20workers%20in%20Arizona%20would%20likely%20be%20forced%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20slack%20for%20their%20American%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20difficult%20thing%20about%20wafer%20manufacturing%20is%20not%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20Wayne%20Chiu%2C%20a%20former%20TSMC%20engineer%20who%20said%20he%20considered%20relocating%20to%20the%20US%20before%20deciding%20against%20it%2C%20told%20the%20Times.%20%26quot%3BThe%20most%20difficult%20thing%20is%20personnel%20management.%20Americans%20are%20the%20worst%20at%20this%20because%20Americans%20are%20the%20most%20difficult%20to%20manage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurrent%20and%20former%20US%20TSMC%20employees%20have%20also%20raised%20concerns%20on%20the%20careers%20site%20Glassdoor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20time%20at%20TSMC%20Phoenix%20was%20a%20nightmare%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Arizona%20engineer%20wrote%20in%20July.%20%26quot%3BThe%20unmanageable%20workload%2C%20toxic%20office%20environment%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20resources%20made%20it%20an%20unbearable%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20anonymous%20Phoenix%20employee%20wrote%20in%20July%3A%20%26quot%3B12-hour%20working%20is%20normal%2C%20it's%20not%20just%20on%20the%20news%2C%20even%20if%20you%20work%20on%20weekends%2C%20still%20can't%20meet%20the%20deadline.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%C2%A0Fortune%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2023%2F06%2F03%2Ftsmc-arizona-plant-jobs-salary-culture-hiring%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20Taiwan%20engineer%20of%20five%20years%20said%20TSMC%20workers%20were%20discouraged%20from%20applying%20for%20overtime%20pay%20and%20expected%20to%20do%20what%20they're%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20impossible%20for%20managers%20to%20express%20their%20opinions%20to%20upper-level%20management.%20This%20simply%20cannot%20be%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2024%2C%20a%20Taiwanese%20YouTube%20channel%20with%20nearly%203%20million%20subscribers%20posted%20a%20video%20accusing%20the%20Arizona%20workers%20of%20being%20lazy%20and%20using%20their%20phones%20too%20much%20on%20the%20job%2C%20a%20bilingual%20newsletter%20on%20tech%2C%20business%2C%20and%20US-Asia%20relations%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkevinsxu%2Fstatus%2F1689639351003848705%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Insider%20was%20unable%20to%20contact%20the%20administrator%20of%20the%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffocustaiwan.tw%2Fbusiness%2F202306070023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFocus%20Taiwan%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20in%20June%20that%20when%20he%20was%20asked%20about%20US%20workers'%20concerns%20about%20the%20company's%20culture%2C%20Mark%20Liu%2C%20TSMC's%20chair%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThose%20who%20are%20unwilling%20to%20take%20shifts%20should%20not%20enter%26quot%3B%20semiconductor%20manufacturing.%26quot%3B%20Liu%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20field%20isn't%20just%20about%20lucrative%20wages%20but%20rather%20a%20passion%20for%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiu%20also%20said%20that%20TSMC's%20US%20workers%20would%20not%20be%20expected%20to%20adopt%20the%20same%20work%20culture%20as%20those%20in%20Taiwan%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20he'd%20be%20open%20to%20changes%20as%20long%20as%20the%20company's%20core%20values%20were%20upheld.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20fierce%20debate%20over%20whether%20US%20workers%20can%20cut%20it%20at%20the%20world's%20leading%20chipmaker%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChang%2C%20TSMC's%20founder%2C%20was%20blunt%20in%20his%20assessment%20of%20the%20US%20workforce%20in%20a%202022%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brookings.edu%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F04%2FVying-for-Talent-Morris-Chang-20220414.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epodcast%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lack%20of%20manufacturing%20talents%20to%20begin%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20cited%20TSMC's%20experience%20at%20its%20Oregon%20manufacturing%20plant%2C%20where%20he%20said%20the%20cost%20of%20production%20was%20about%2050%25%20higher%20than%20in%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20send%20all%20kinds%20of%20people.%20We%20change%20the%20managers%2C%20change%20the%20engineers.%20We%20use%20both%20America%2C%20local%20engineers.%20We%20also%20send%20engineers%20from%20Taiwan%20to%20Oregon%20to%20try%20to%20improve%20the%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20the%20podcast%2C%20hosted%20by%20the%20Brookings%20Institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20performance%20had%20improved%20but%20that%20the%2050%25%20cost%20difference%20remained%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20claiming%20a%20skills%20shortage%20in%20Phoenix%2C%20TSMC%20has%20deliberately%20misrepresented%20the%20skillset%20of%20Arizona's%20workforce%2C%20Arizona%20Pipe%20Trades%20469%20Union%20said.%20It%20says%20it%20represents%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fazpipetrades.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eover%204%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20pipe%20fitters%2C%20plumbers%2C%20welders%2C%20and%20heating%2C%20ventilation%2C%20and%20air-conditioning%20technicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20started%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.votervoice.net%2FAZPipeTrades%2FCampaigns%2F106830%2FRespond%3Futm_source%3Dsubstack%26utm_medium%3Demail%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epetition%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20urge%20US%20lawmakers%20to%20deny%20the%20Taiwanese%20worker%20visas%20the%20company%20was%20seeking.%20By%20approving%20TSMC's%20visa%20requests%2C%20the%20union%20said%2C%20lawmakers%20would%20be%20laying%20the%20groundwork%20for%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprotectazworkers.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echeap%20labor%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20to%20replace%20American%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReplacing%20Arizona's%20construction%20workers%20with%20foreign%20construction%20workers%20directly%20contradicts%20the%20very%20purpose%20for%20which%20the%20CHIPS%20Act%20was%20enacted%20%E2%80%94%20to%20create%20jobs%20for%20American%20workers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petition%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20union%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%2C%20and%20TSMC%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20questions%20about%20its%20culture%20and%20expectations%20for%20US%20workers.%20However%2C%20the%20company%20did%20say%20that%20the%20incoming%20Taiwanese%20workers%20will%20not%20be%20a%20threat%20to%20any%20US%20jobs%20%E2%80%94%20and%20be%20there%20for%20only%20a%20limited%20time%20to%20support%20the%20construction%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20TSMC%20Arizona%20fab%20is%20now%20in%20a%20critical%20phase%20of%20handling%20and%20installing%20all%20of%20the%20most%20advanced%20and%20dedicated%20equipment%20in%20a%20sophisticated%20facility%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20told%20Insider%2C%20citing%20the%20deployment%20of%20giant%20and%20complex%20tools.%20%26quot%3BOur%20vendors%20need%20to%20mobilize%20specialized%20workers%20with%20strong%20experience%20and%20related%20skillsets%20to%20support%20this%20work%20and%20share%20the%20knowledge%20with%20the%20local%20workers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20not%20replaced%20any%20of%20our%20local%20workers%20with%20foreign%20workers%20and%20continue%20to%20prioritize%20the%20hiring%20of%20local%20workers%20in%20Arizona.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdam%20Ozimek%2C%20an%20Economic%20Innovation%20Group%20economist%2C%20recently%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FModeledBehavior%2Fstatus%2F1690071675834908672%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20X%2C%20the%20platform%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter%2C%20that%20Americans%20might%20be%20able%20to%20do%20the%20work%20%E2%80%94%20but%20at%20a%20slower%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20have%20heard%20from%20semiconductor%20industry%20people%20is%20that%20it%20isn't%20that%20US%20plumbers%20and%20pipe-fitters%20literally%20can't%20do%20the%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20that%20it%20takes%20them%20an%20order%20of%20magnitude%20longer%20because%20of%20experience%20differences.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20work%20in%20the%20semiconductor%20chip%20industry%20and%20have%20a%20story%20to%20tell%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%228fb9ce7f5f77b7c71300026184abf261%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajzinkula%40insider.com%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajzinkula%40insider.com%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3Ejzinkula%40insider.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsmc-jobs-taiwan-semiconductor-chip-worker-skills-work-ethic-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692180001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64db796c1f51cc001969c048%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsmc-jobs-taiwan-semiconductor-chip-worker-skills-work-ethic-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jobs%20at%20the%20TSMC%20semiconductor%20factory%20in%20Arizona%20could%20require%20long%20hours%20and%20total%20obedience.%20Americans%20may%20push%20back%20on%20the%20company's%20culture.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jzinkula%40insider.com%20(Jacob%20Zinkula)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsmc-jobs-taiwan-semiconductor-chip-worker-skills-work-ethic-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222%20Gen%20Xers%20who%20joined%20the%20wave%20of%20Americans%20moving%20to%20Austria%20explain%20how%20it's%20improved%20their%20quality%20of%20life%20and%20given%20them%20a%20fresh%20start%20in%20their%20careers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22(Left)%20Rick%20Lewis%20stands%20with%20his%20daughter%3B%20(Right)%20Michael%20Valentine%20on%20a%20hike%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64da91a15e5d5a00195ddb27%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELeft%2C%20Rick%20Lewis%20stands%20with%20his%20daughter.%20Right%2C%20Michael%20Valentine%20on%20a%20hike.%3Cp%3ERick%20Lewis%2FMichael%20Valentine%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETwo%20Gen%20Xers%20who%20moved%20to%20Austria%20from%20the%20US%20said%20they%20had%20more%20freedom%20and%20fewer%20anxieties.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20move%20has%20given%20the%20two%20dads%20more%20time%20to%20spend%20with%20family%20and%20travel%20across%20Europe.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMany%20Americans%20have%20recently%20moved%20to%20cities%20such%20as%20Vienna%20and%20Innsbruck%20for%20work%20opportunities.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Michael%20Valentine%20was%20laid%20off%20in%202018%20from%20his%20leadership%20position%20at%20a%20robotics%20company%20in%20Michigan%2C%20he%20was%20devastated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20some%20thought%2C%20the%2053-year-old%20decided%20to%20move%20up%20his%20retirement%20plans%20and%20relocate%20to%20his%20wife's%20home%20country%20of%20Austria.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20their%20daughter%2C%20the%20couple%20opened%20a%20women's%20fashion%20store%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Innsbruck%2C%20where%20everyone%20gets%20a%20minimum%20of%20five%20weeks%20guaranteed%20paid%20leave%20and%20frequent%20holidays.%20He%20said%20he's%20relieved%20the%20nation's%20work%20culture%20was%20less%20intense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20belief%20here%20that%20vacation%20is%20something%20that%20you%20have%20to%20do%20for%20your%20own%20mental%20health%20to%20make%20you%20a%20better%2C%20more%20productive%20employee%2C%26quot%3B%20Valentine%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20different%20philosophy%20from%20the%20US%20in%20that%20when%20you%20go%20on%20vacation%2C%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20you're%20checking%20your%20email%20all%20the%20time%20or%20taking%20phone%20calls.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20Americans%20are%20moving%20to%20Austria%20recently%20for%20employment%20opportunities%20and%20to%20improve%20their%20quality%20of%20life.%20Recent%20college%20graduates%20and%2030-year%20professionals%20alike%20told%20Insider%20they're%20are%20making%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvienna-austria-worlds-most-livable-city-ranking-economist-auckland-europe-2022-6%5C%22%3Emove%20to%20cities%20such%20as%20Vienna%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Linz%2C%20a%20decision%20that%20two%20dads%20said%20was%20well%20worth%20the%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20have%20moved%20to%20Austria%20to%20fill%20jobs%20the%20Austrian%20government%20has%20listed%20as%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.migration.gv.at%2Fen%2Ftypes-of-immigration%2Fpermanent-immigration%2Faustria-wide-shortage-occupations%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshortage%20occupations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20include%20engineers%2C%20nurses%2C%20and%20bakers.%20One%20estimate%20puts%20the%20number%20of%20Americans%20living%20in%20Austria%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbrighttax.com%2Fblog%2Fus-expat-taxes-for-americans-living-in-austria-everything-you-need-to-know%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIt%2520has%2520been%2520estimated%2520that%2Cthe%2520parks%252C%2520and%2520the%2520skiing.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20over%2011%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20most%20countries%2C%20it%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20get%20jobs%20that%20they%20feel%20like%20a%20local%20could%20do%2C%20and%20that's%20a%20real%20struggle%20for%20folks%20who%20don't%20have%20degree%20skills%20or%20credential%20skills%2C%26quot%3B%20Jen%20Barnett%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fexpatsi.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EExpatsi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20provides%20services%20for%20US%20expats%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20notable%20that%20they%20are%20hiring%20for%20entry-level%20roles%20that%20don't%20require%20a%20degree%20and%20or%20an%20apprenticeship.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarnett%20said%20Austria's%20high%20English%20proficiency%2C%20temperate%20weather%2C%20and%20progressive%20policies%20toward%20women%20and%20LGBTQ%2B%20communities%20had%20been%20major%20pulls.%20Austria%20also%20ranks%20in%20the%20top%2010%20globally%20for%20safety%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20infrastructure%2C%20which%20Barnett%20said%20was%20%26quot%3Bsuper%20rare.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Valentine%2C%20it's%20the%20relaxed%20lifestyle%2C%20including%20more%20time%20off%20and%20access%20to%20nature%2C%20that%20makes%20him%20happy%20in%20his%20new%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20any%20interest%20in%20leaving%20Austria%2C%26quot%3B%20Valentine%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20America%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20miss%20living%20in%20America.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20dad%20says%20his%20mental%20health%20improved%20after%204%20years%20in%20Innsbruck%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Michael%20Valentine%20on%20a%20hike%20in%20the%20Alps%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64da92261f51cc0019695e7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EValentine%20on%20a%20hike%20in%20the%20Alps.%3Cp%3EMichael%20Valentine%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EValentine%C2%A0said%20the%20move%20softened%20years%20of%20work-related%20anxiety.%20Getting%20to%20traverse%20the%20Alps%2C%20easily%20travel%20to%20Italy%20and%20Croatia%2C%20and%20spend%20more%20time%20with%20his%20family%20are%20all%20welcome%20changes%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20studying%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Innsbruck%20in%20Austria%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20the%20Detroit%20native%20started%20a%20robotics%20company%20in%20the%20US%20with%20his%20brother%2C%20then%20joined%20another%20company%20in%20Michigan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EValentine%20acknowledged%20he%20made%20higher%20wages%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20the%20family%20lives%20in%20a%20smaller%20home%20than%20they%20could%20have%20afforded%20in%20the%20US.%20In%20his%20case%2C%20though%2C%20the%20quality-of-life%20improvements%20were%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20Austria's%20stores%20are%20mostly%20closed%20on%20Sundays%2C%20he%20said%20the%20family%20had%20an%20extra%20day%20to%20not%20worry%20about%20the%20shop%20and%20focus%20on%20enjoying%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EValentine%20initially%20feared%20his%20high-school-age%20daughter%2C%20who%20was%20adopted%20from%20China%2C%20would%20face%20discrimination%20in%20Austria%2C%20he%20said%2C%20but%20she%20has%20integrated%20well%20at%20her%20public%20international%20school.%20His%20daughter%20will%20be%20able%20to%20attend%20most%20European%20universities%20for%20almost%20free%2C%20which%20he%20estimated%20would%20save%20the%20family%20over%20%24150%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20gets%20older%2C%20he%20added%2C%20being%20in%20a%20country%20with%20reliable%20and%20inexpensive%20healthcare%20has%20brought%20him%20peace%20of%20mind.%20He%20said%20one%20time%2C%20he%20broke%20his%20wrist%20and%20was%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20hospital%20with%20a%20cast%20in%2045%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20his%20family%20had%20cut%20down%20on%20transit%20costs.%20For%20example%2C%20they%20have%20only%20one%20car%20since%20public%20transportation%20is%20fast%20and%20convenient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EValentine%20said%20the%20adjustment%20to%20Austrian%20life%20came%20with%20its%20ups%20and%20downs%2C%20such%20as%20relearning%20some%20norms%20and%20getting%20acclimated%20again%20to%20the%20formalities%20of%20the%20German%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20one%20thing%20to%20be%20able%20to%20go%20someplace%20and%20survive%20and%20get%20by%20on%20a%20day-to-day%20level%2C%20but%20to%20get%20to%20where%20you're%20thriving%20and%20get%20to%20know%20people%20and%20do%20things%2C%20it's%20important%20where%20you%20should%20learn%20the%20language%2C%26quot%3B%20Valentine%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20dad%20who%20lives%20in%20a%20small%20town%20in%20the%20Alps%20says%20the%20laid-back%20workweek%20has%20made%20Austria%20his%20'landing%20spot'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rick%20Lewis%20with%20his%20daughter%20in%20the%20Alps%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64da92625e5d5a00195ddc6c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELewis%20with%20his%20daughter%20in%20the%20Alps.%3Cp%3ERick%20Lewis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERick%20Lewis%2C%20an%20Ohio%20native%20who%20lives%20with%20his%20daughter%20in%20a%20small%20Austrian%20town%20in%20the%20Alps%2C%20said%20the%20country's%20laid-back%20lifestyle%20and%20work-life%20balance%20had%20led%20him%20to%20decide%20to%20stay%20for%20the%20long%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20it%20wasn't%20an%20economic%20decision%3B%20it%20was%20more%20a%20life%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20Lewis%2C%20who%20has%20lived%20in%20South%20Korea%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20Russia%2C%20and%20the%20Bahamas%20for%20his%20work%20as%20an%20educator%20and%20school%20administrator%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20visa%20process%20and%20apartment%20hunt%20were%20somewhat%20difficult%20to%20navigate%2C%20Lewis%20said%20his%20quality%20of%20life%20skyrocketed%20as%20he%20switched%20from%2010-%20to%2012-hour%20workdays%20at%20previous%20schools%20to%20shorter%20days%20with%20frequent%20vacation%20days.%20Though%20he%20works%20five%20days%20a%20week%2C%20most%20teachers%20at%20his%20school%20work%20four-day%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20lot%20of%20Austrians%2C%20they%20might%20take%20an%2080%25%20job%20or%20a%2070%25%20job%20instead%20of%20working%20full%20time%20since%20they%20have%20a%20kid%20at%20home%20or%20they%20have%20other%20things%20going%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20Lewis%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20many%20people%20worked%20just%2020%20hours%20a%20week%20across%20multiple%20part-time%20jobs.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20that%20they%20don't%20care%20about%20how%20much%20money%20they're%20making%3B%20it's%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20in%20terms%20of%20how%20much%20they%20want%20to%20work.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20natural%20beauty%20of%20the%20mountains%20and%20the%20calm%20but%20efficient%20lifestyle%20didn't%20hurt%2C%20Lewis%20said.%20He%20said%20he%20quickly%20came%20to%20know%20everyone%20in%20his%20town%20%E2%80%94%20partly%20because%20he%20always%20wears%20baseball%20hats%20%E2%80%94%20and%20integrated%20into%20the%20community%20through%20local%20festivals%20and%20charity%20events.%20Though%20he%20doesn't%20speak%20German%2C%20Lewis%20said%20there%20were%20a%20handful%20of%20other%20expats%20living%20close%20by%20who%20helped%20each%20other%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20laid-back%20workweek%20has%20afforded%20Lewis%20the%20opportunity%20to%20take%20on%20extra%20work%20with%20schools%20in%20Africa%2C%20as%20well%20as%20spend%20more%20time%20with%20family.%20He%20said%20the%20freedom%20to%20hop%20on%20a%20train%20or%20hang%20out%20with%20his%20daughter%20was%20unlike%20the%20rigid%20work%20environment%20of%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20my%20landing%20spot%2C%26quot%3B%20Lewis%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'll%20keep%20working%20here%20until%20I%20retire%2C%20no%20doubt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustria-innsbruck-alps-expat-moving-work-life-balance-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692180001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64da91a15e5d5a00195ddb27%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustria-innsbruck-alps-expat-moving-work-life-balance-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20Gen%20X%20dads%20told%20Insider%20that%20after%20moving%20to%20Austria%2C%20they%20had%20more%20time%20to%20spend%20with%20family%2C%20travel%20more%20frequently%2C%20and%20enjoy%20nature.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nsheidlower%40insider.com%20(Noah%20Sheidlower)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustria-innsbruck-alps-expat-moving-work-life-balance-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22