ike%20that%20in%20Florida.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mary%20Cannon's%20son%20on%20a%20boat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dbd4ab5e5d5a00195eab1f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECannon's%20son%20on%20a%20boat.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Mary%20Cannon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMonths%20out%20of%20the%20year%20I%20find%20myself%20unable%20to%20enjoy%20being%20outdoors%20due%20to%20the%20heat.%20My%20family%20and%20I%20go%20to%20Disney%20World%20on%20a%20regular%20basis%20and%20I've%20seen%20things%20that%20I%20don't%20remember%20witnessing%20growing%20up%2C%20like%20people%20begging%20for%20ice%20or%20fainting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20weather%20is%20nicer%20in%20North%20Carolina%20and%20my%20son%20thrives%20here%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20chose%20to%20purchase%20a%20second%20home%20in%20North%20Carolina%20because%20of%20the%20state's%20beauty%20and%20its%20hospitable%20climate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20purchased%20a%20%24775%2C000%20home%20that%20sits%20on%2029%20acres.%20The%20home%20was%20built%20in%201994%20and%20is%20way%20bigger%20than%20our%20home%20in%20Orlando.%20In%20Orlando%2C%20we%20own%20a%20three-bedroom%2C%20one-and-a-half-bathroom%20home%20that%20my%20husband%20purchased%20in%201994%20for%20%2494%2C500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20home%20in%20Hayesville%20has%20five%20bedrooms%20and%20four%20bathrooms.%20It%20comes%20with%20a%20basement%20apartment%2C%20a%20creek%20in%20the%20backyard%2C%20a%20100-foot%20waterfall%2C%20and%20a%20porch%20where%20we%20can%20soak%20up%20the%20sunlight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mary%20Cannon's%20property%20in%20North%20Carolina.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dbd3635e5d5a00195ea904%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECannon's%20property%20in%20North%20Carolina.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Mary%20Cannon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20droves%20of%20Floridians%20moving%20to%20North%20Carolina%2C%20and%20the%20locals%20don't%20particularly%20like%20that.%20Nevertheless%2C%20we've%20started%20making%20some%20friends%20in%20the%20city.%20This%20year%2C%20we%20met%20some%20neighbors%20who%20we%20expected%20to%20be%20locals%2C%20but%20it%20turns%20out%20they're%20from%20Florida.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20Florida%2C%20life%20in%20Hayesville%20feels%20like%20heaven.%20When%20my%20family%20and%20I%20come%20into%20town%2C%20I%20can%20feel%20a%20physical%20change.%20I%20have%20more%20relaxed%20breathing%20and%20tension%20leaves%20my%20body.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20son%20also%20thrives%20in%20Hayesville.%20I'm%20noticing%20a%20huge%20difference%20in%20his%20development%20when%20we're%20here%20versus%20when%20we're%20in%20Orlando.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mary's%20son%20at%20annual%20tractor%20parade%20in%20Hayesville.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dbd4634ef9f30019f784ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECannon's%20son%20at%20annual%20tractor%20parade%20in%20Hayesville.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Mary%20Cannon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20fun%2C%20my%20family%20and%20I%20like%20to%20hang%20out%20in%20Hayesville's%20downtown%20area%2C%20which%20has%20a%20historic%20town%20square.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20outdoor%20activities%2C%20we%20go%20for%20walks%20or%20hang%20out%20in%20our%20own%20backyard.%20The%20wildlife%20here%20is%20incredible%20and%20we've%20seen%20bears%2C%20pigs%2C%20turkeys%20and%20deers%20at%20our%20house.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20for%20our%20mental%20health%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20be%20outside%20in%20nature%20versus%20being%20cooped%20up%20in%20a%20box%20all%20day