title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Lt%20Governor%20Objects%20To%20Assembly%20Session%20That%20May%20Debate%20Services%20Law%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20assembly%20session%20convened%20today%20has%20become%20the%20latest%20flashpoint%20between%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%20and%20the%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lt%20Governor%20has%20objected%20to%20the%20two-day%20assembly%20session%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20see%20a%20heated%20debate%20on%20a%20central%20law%20that%20took%20away%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20control%20over%20postings%20and%20transfers%20of%20officers%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parliament-enacted%20law%20replaced%20an%20ordinance%20enforced%20by%20the%20government%2C%20triggering%20sharp%20responses%20from%20the%20AAP%20and%20the%20extended%20Opposition%20camp.%20The%20AAP%20had%20also%20challenged%20the%20Bill%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERakhi%20Birla%2C%20Deputy%20Speaker%20of%20the%20Assembly%2C%20said%20Mr%20Saxena%20expressed%20his%20objection%20in%20an%20August%2011%20letter%20to%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20was%20given%20to%20the%20assembly%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lt%20Governor%20claimed%20the%20assembly%20session%20was%20called%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20rules%2C%20and%20a%20session%20is%20not%20prorogued%20but%20run%20in%20several%20parts%2C%20said%20Ms%20Birla%2C%20and%20chose%20to%20differ%20with%20his%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Delhi%20Assembly%20is%20running%20completely%20under%20the%20rules.%20It%20is%20the%20prerogative%20of%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20when%20to%20call%20a%20session.%20The%20Lt%20Governor%20has%20made%20a%20serious%20allegation.%20He%20should%20know%20a%20new%20session%20cannot%20be%20called%20unless%20the%20cabinet%20recommends%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20Birla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20further%20said%20that%20the%20NCT%20Act%2C%20which%20provides%20a%20framework%20for%20running%20the%20Delhi%20Assembly%2C%20has%20no%20provision%20that%20makes%20it%20compulsory%20to%20call%20Budget%2C%20Monsoon%20and%20Winter%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20of%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20Delhi%20Services%20Act%2C%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20parliament%20during%20the%20Monsoon%20Session%20and%20later%20accorded%20the%20President's%20assent.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20AAP%2C%20had%20accused%20the%20centre%20of%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Busurp%26quot%3B%20power%20through%20backdoor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Delhi%20Services%20Minister%20Atishi%20said%20today%20her%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20respect%20the%20central%20law%20until%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20takes%20a%20decision%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20government%20had%20called%20a%20special%20assembly%20session%20in%20April%20too%2C%20after%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20summoned%20by%20the%20CBI%20in%20an%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20case%2C%20in%20which%20his%20former%20deputy%20Manish%20Sisodia%20was%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lt%20Governor%2C%20then%20too%2C%20had%20objected%20to%20the%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692179700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2Frth526i8_vk-saxena-kejriwal_625x300_20_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Ftodays-delhi-assembly-session-latest-flashpoint-between-aap-lt-governor-4302114%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20assembly%20session%20convened%20today%20has%20become%20the%20latest%20flashpoint%20between%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%20and%20the%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Ftodays-delhi-assembly-session-latest-flashpoint-between-aap-lt-governor-4302114%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Ftodays-delhi-assembly-session-latest-flashpoint-between-aap-lt-governor-4302114%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Ftodays-delhi-assembly-session-latest-flashpoint-between-aap-lt-governor-4302114%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Red%20Flag%5C%22%3A%20After%20Alia's%20Lipstick%20Demo%2C%20The%20Internet%20Is%20Going%20After%20Ranbir%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBollywood's%20IT%20couple%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsearch%3Fsearchtext%3DAlia-Bhatt-and-Ranbir-Kapoor%5C%22%3EAlia%20Bhatt%20and%20Ranbir%20Kapoo%3C%2Fa%3Er%20are%20making%20headlines%20again%20but%20not%20really%20for%20the%20right%20reasons.%20The%20%3Cem%3EWake%20Up%20Sid%20s%3C%2Fem%3Etar%20is%20getting%20trolled%20on%20social%20media%20after%20Alia%20Bhatt%20made%20a%20revelation%20about%20him%20in%20a%20recent%20video%20for%20Vogue.%20As%20part%20of%20her%20%3Cem%3EHeart%20Of%20Stone%20%3C%2Fem%3Epromotions%2C%20Alia%20Bhatt%20shared%20her%20%E2%80%9Cbeauty%20secrets%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20video.%20Towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20clip%2C%20the%20actress%20revealed%20that%20she%20has%20a%20peculiar%20way%20of%20applying%20lipsticks.%20She%20moves%20her%20lip%20and%20not%20the%20lipstick%20during%20application%20she%20said%2C%20demonstrating%20the%20same%20in%20the%20clip.%20Alia%20is%20then%20seen%20wiping%20off%20the%20lipstick%20to%20leave%20just%20a%20stain.%20Explaining%20why%20she%20does%20so%2C%20Alia%20said%20that%20her%20husband%20(Ranbir)%20would%20ask%20her%20to%20%26quot%3Bwipe%20off%26quot%3B%C2%A0her%20lipstick%20because%20he%20liked%20her%20natural%20lip%20shade%20when%20they%20would%20step%20out%20for%20dates%20during%20their%20courtship%20period.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlia%20Bhatt%20can%20be%20heard%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20then%2C%20I%20rub%20it%20off.%20Because%20one%20thing%20my%20husband%20%5Bwhen%20he%20wasn't%20my%20husband%20when%20he%20was%20my%20boyfriend%20as%20well%5D%20says%20when%20we%20used%20to%20go%20out%20at%20night%2C%20he%20used%20to%20say%20'Wipe%20that%20%5Blipstick%5D%20off.%20Wipe%20that%20off'.%20Because%20he%20loves%20the%20natural%20colour%20of%20my%20lip.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20video%20shared%20on%20the%20official%20Vogue%20Instagram%20page%2C%20several%20fans%20expressed%20their%20displeasure%20over%20how%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20was%20exercising%20his%20opinion%20on%20Alia%20Bhatt's%20lipstick%20choices.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20more%20I%20listen%20about%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20the%20more%20I%20feel%20scared%20for%20her.%20If%20your%20bf%2Fhusband%20is%20telling%20you%20to%20wipe%20your%20lipstick%20that%20is%20the%20biggest%20sign%20for%20you%20to%20run!%20It%20is%20not%20cute%20or%20funny%20at%20all!%20Can%20not%20believe%20the%20most%20celebrated%20actress%20at%20this%20moment%20of%20India%20is%20going%20through%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20fan%20pointed%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20literally%20glorifying%20such%20misogynistic%20behaviour.%20But%20why%3F%20Well%2C%20she%20might%20think%20it's%20cute%20but%20it's%20not.%20Her%20husband%20doesn't%20like%20it%20if%20her%20voice%20goes%20above%20a%20certain%20decibel%2C%20her%20husband%20legit%20orders%20her%20to%20wipe%20off%20the%20lipstick%20she%20be%20wearing.%20Based%20on%20how%20she's%20narrating%2C%20it%20smells%20like%20misogyny%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20another%20fan%2C%20referring%20to%20another%20interview%20where%20Alia%20Bhatt%20said%20that%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20does%20not%20like%20it%20when%20she%20talks%20too%20loudly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20can't%20believe%20a%20top%20actress%20of%20her%20time%20rubs%20off%20her%20expensive%20lipstick%20because%20her%20%26quot%3Bbf%2Fhusband%26quot%3B%20tells%20her%20to%20rub%20it%20off%2C%E2%80%9D%20another%20user%20said.%20A%20user%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20husband%2C%20my%20wedding%20-