0UPS%20driver%20in%20Rhode%20Island.%20Her%20last%20name%20has%20been%20omitted%20for%20privacy%20reasons.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Teamsters%20union%20secured%20a%20win%20guaranteeing%20that%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fups-170k-deal-driver-job-searches-soar-union-wage-increase-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20UPS%20delivery%20drivers%20would%20make%20%24170%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20salary%20and%20benefits%20by%20the%20end%20of%20a%205-year%20period%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-workers-comments-170k-ups-driver-deal-anger-admiration-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeople%20in%20tech%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20white-collar%20workers%20had%20a%20lot%20to%20say%20about%20it.%20As%20the%20wife%20of%20a%20UPS%20driver%2C%20so%20do%20I.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20start%20with%20the%20facts.%20The%20%24170%2C000%20is%20not%20a%20base%20salary%20%E2%80%94%20it%20takes%20into%20consideration%20healthcare%20and%20pension%20benefits.%20But%20that's%20not%20even%20what%20bothers%20me%20most%20about%20people's%20reactions%2C%20which%20range%20from%20wondering%20why%20drivers%20would%20make%20that%20much%20money%20to%20calling%20them%20overpaid%20and%20undeserving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20really%20want%20people%20to%20think%20about%20why%20they%20believe%20UPS%20workers%20don't%20deserve%20to%20be%20fairly%20compensated%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20seems%20like%20a%20lot%20of%20it%20has%20to%20do%20with%20the%20snobbery%20white-collar%20workers%20feel%20toward%20blue-collar%20workers.%20I'm%20a%20hairdresser%20so%20I%20see%20it%20in%20my%20work%2C%20too.%20Some%20people%20just%20feel%20like%20they're%20better%20than%20us%20and%20that%20we%20don't%20deserve%20nice%20things%20or%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%