ave%20any%20idea%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fups-driver-loves-job-hates-drama-office-politics-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhat%20it's%20like%20to%20be%20a%20UPS%20driver%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I%20do%20because%20I%20see%20it%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEditor's%20note%3A%20A%20UPS%20spokesperson%20sent%20the%20following%20statement%20to%20Insider%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EThe%20safety%20and%20well-being%20of%20every%20UPSer%20is%20our%20top%20priority.%20We%20have%20been%20steadily%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabout.ups.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Four-company%2Fgreat-employer%2F5-ways-ups-is-improving-heat-safety-for-employees.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ebuilding%20on%20our%20efforts%20to%20protect%20our%20people%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20in%20the%20face%20of%20increasingly%20hot%20temperatures%2C%20provide%20a%20safe%20work%20environment%2C%20and%20make%20working%20at%20UPS%20a%20great%20experience%20for%20employees%20as%20they%20serve%20our%20customers%20and%20strengthen%20our%20communities.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20worked%20with%20top%20experts%20in%20heat%20safety%20to%20study%20our%20working%20conditions%20and%20further%20improve%20our%20trainings%20and%20protocols%20to%20help%20our%20employees%20work%20safely%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20on%20hot%20days.%20Improvements%20include%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EProviding%20and%20encouraging%20our%20employees%20to%20take%20appropriate%20breaks%20as%20needed.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EA%20focus%20on%20how%20to%20prevent%20heat%20stress%20from%20occurring%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fl