t%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDamian%20Simon%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20for%20London%20Blitz%20Clean%20for%202015%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Damian%20Simon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDamian%20Simon%20set%20up%20London%20Blitz%20Clean%20in%202015%20to%20help%20hoarders%20clear%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20often%20gets%20bookings%20from%20local%20authorities%20so%20people%20don't%20live%20in%20unsafe%20properties.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20some%20people%20hoard%20bodily%20fluids%2C%20trash%20bags%2C%20and%20food%20waste.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20as-told-to%20essay%20based%20on%20an%20interview%20with%20Damian%20Simon%2C%20a%20former%20care%20worker%20who%20set%20up%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flondonblitzclean.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3ELondon%20Blitz%20Clean%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%20company%20that%20helps%20hoarders%20clear%20their%20homes.%20Insider%20has%20verified%20his%20current%20company%20and%20previous%20employment%20with%20documentation.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20worked%20in%20the%20care%20industry%20for%20around%2020%20years%2C%20first%20as%20a%20care%20worker%2C%20then%20as%20a%20manager%20helping%20to%20care%20for%20people%20who%20are%20unwell%2C%20elderly%2C%20or%20have%20disabilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20time%20we%20would%20often%20get%20asked%20by%20local%20authorities%20to%20have%20carers%20assist%20people%20who%20were%20being%20discharged%20from%20hospital.%20It%20was%20quite%20common%20for%20some%20carers%20to%20refuse%20to%20work%20in%20homes%20that%20were%20extremely%20unsanitary%20and%20cluttered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20meant%20patients%20were%20kept%20in%20hospitals%20longer%20as%20they%20couldn't%20be%20discharged%20to%20an%20unsafe%20property%2C%20putting%20further%20strain%20on%20the%20National%20Health%20Service%2C%20which%20was%20already%20stretched%20and%20in%20need%20of%20spare%20beds.%20I%20realized%20that%20this%20was%20costing%20the%20NHS%20more%20and%20that%20led%20me%20to%20come%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20for%20the%20cleaning%20company%20London%20Blitz%20Clean%20in%202015%20to%20try%20and%20solve%20these%20problems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20it%20was%20just%20myself%20and%20another%20former%20care%20worker%20who%20would%20do%20odd%20cleaning%20jobs.%20Then%20I%20got%20a%20call%20from%20a%20local%20London%20council%20asking%20for%20help%20with%20a%20big%20cleaning%20job%20for%20a%20hoarder.%20That%20council%20came%20back%20with%20another%20job%20a%20month%20later%20and%20before%20I%20knew%20it%2C%20we%20grew%20from%20there%20and%20I%20had%20five%20care%20managers%20booking%20jobs%20with%20us.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20often%20called%20to%20homes%20that%20have%20been%20neglected.%20This%20could%20be%20where%20someone%20is%20using%20the%20kitchen%20to%20make%20meals%20but%20they%20don't%20clean%20up%20for%20months%20and%20then%20there's%20a%20huge%20build-up%20of%20trash.%20That%20can%20come%20in%20various%20levels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20might%20just%20have%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20mess%20or%20there%20could%20be%20floor-to-ceiling%20trash.%20Every%20single%20job%20is%20different.%20There%20are%20also%20examples%20of%20people%20living%20in%20neglect%20and%20hoarding%20deposits%20of%20bodily%20fluids.%20From%20experience%2C%20around%20one%20in%20every%2016%20jobs%20people%20have%20hoarded%20feces%20and%20urine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20one%20job%20where%20a%20guy%20was%20renting%20an%20apartment%20and%20he'd%20smashed%20all%20the%20windows%2C%20plug%20sockets%2C%20and%20doors%20and%20kept%20rubbish%20stacked%20up%20to%20knee%20height.%20He%20was%20using%20the%20toilet%20but%20not%20flushing%20it.%20When%20it%20wasn't%20working%2C%20he%20kicked%20the%20toilet%20off%20the%20hinges%20and%20defecated%20in%20the%20outer%20pipe%20until%20it%20couldn't%20take%20it%20anymore.%20He%20didn't%20get%20it%20fixed%2C%20instead%2C%20he%20bought%20buckets%20and%20portable%20commodes%20and%20filled%20every%20single%20one%20of%20them%2C%20and%20then%20left%20the%20apartment.%20I%20had%20a%20team%20of%20three%20people%20clean%20that%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20collage%20of%20a%20dirty%20and%20clean%20toilet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cf9a83f5d4870019e28399%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20before%20and%20after%20photo%20of%20a%20toilet%20at%20a%20property%20Simon%20had%20cleaned%3Cp%3EDamian%20Simon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20three%20teams%20of%20cleaning%20crew%20that%20are%20made%20up%20of%20two%20people%20each%20who%20work%20together%20to%20complete%20a%20job.%20Most%20jobs%20can%20be%20done%20in%20a%20day%2C%20but%20the%20most%20extreme%20ones%20can%20take%20around%20two%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20take%20the%20trash%20bags%20to%20landfills%20using%20an%20unmarked%20truck%2C%20so%20as%20not%20to%20cause%20embarrassment%20for%20people.%20We%20try%20to%20be%20as%20sensitive%20and%20empathetic%20as%20possible%20toward%20people%20living%20in%20severe%20neglect%20as%20we%20often%20hear%20from%20them%20that%20they're%20embarrassed.%20Most%20hoarders%20are%20often%20older%2C%20but%20we%20do%20also%20work%20with%20people%20in%20their%2020s%20and%20upward.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20worst%20cases%20I've%20seen%20were%20an%20old%20lady%20who%20died%20in%20her%20apartment%20during%20the%20summer%20when%20it%20was%20extremely%20hot%2C%20and%20another%20person%20who%20has%20a%20seizure%20and%20died%20in%20the%20bedroom%20at%20around%20the%20same%20time.%20No%20one%20had%20visited%20their%20homes%20so%20their%20bodies%20decomposed%20in%20the%20heat%20and%20had%20essentially%20melted%20through%20the%20floor%20into%20the%20neighbor's%20home%20below.%20There%20were%20millions%20of%20flies.%20I've%20never%20seen%20anything%20like%20it%20and%20the%20stench%20was%20unbearable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20may%20hoard%20cardboard%20boxes%2C%20comic%20books%2C%20and%20other%20items%2C%20while%20others%20hoard%20trash.%20We%20once%20went%20to%20a%20property%20where%20six%20dead%20cats%20were%20found%20at%20various%20stages%20of%20decomposition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20experience%2C%20people%20who%20hoard%20and%20live%20in%20these%20environments%20often%20have%20severe%20mental%20health%20disorders.%20Some%20have%20told%20me%20that%20keeping%20their%20homes%20clean%20was%20difficult%20as%20it%20%26quot%3Bjust%20got%20on%20top%20of%20me.%26quot%3B%20Others%20have%20been%20unaware%20of%20how%20bad%20their%20living%20conditions%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20some%20people%20say%20we've%20saved%20their%20lives%20after%20we%20completed%20jobs%2C%20and%20that%20they%20never%20could%20have%20done%20it%20themselves.%20They%20say%20they%20feel%20much%20more%20positive%20in%20their%20lives%20and%20that%20their%20mental%20health%20has%20improved.%20It's%20good%20to%20know%20we're%20helping%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcleaning-company-helps-hoarders-clean-unsanitary-messy-homes-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692177148000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cf99e120f1cf0019cb7441%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcleaning-company-helps-hoarders-clean-unsanitary-messy-homes-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Damian%20Simon%20said%20hoarders%20often%20suffer%20with%20mental%20health%20disorders.%20The%20company%20tries%20to%20be%20as%