ve%20is%20not%20to%20criticise%20those%20judgments%20or%20doubt%20them.%20This%20is%20just%20to%20underline%20how%20gender%20stereotypes%20are%20perpetuated%20inadvertently.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20stereotypes%20may%20impact%20judicial%20decision-making%2C%20the%20handbook%20states%2C%20%26quot%3BLike%20any%20person%2C%20a%20judge%20may%20also%20unconsciously%20hold%20or%20rely%20on%20stereotypes.%20If%20a%20judge%20relies%20on%20preconceived%20assumptions%20about%20people%20or%20groups%20when%20deciding%20cases%20or%20writing%20judgements%2C%20the%20harm%20caused%20can%20be%20enormous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20when%20judges%20reach%20legally%20correct%20outcomes%2C%20the%20use%20of%20reasoning%20or%20language%20that%20promotes%20gender%20stereotypes%20undermines%20the%20unique%20characteristics%2C%20autonomy%2C%20and%20dignity%20of%20the%20individuals%20before%20the%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20stated%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20use%20of%20stereotypes%20by%20judges%20also%20has%20the%20effect%20of%20entrenching%20and%20perpetuating%20stereotypes%2C%20creating%20a%20vicious%20cycle%20of%20injustice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EListing%20several%20stereotypical%20words%20and%20their%20alternatives%2C%20the%20handbook%20stated%20that%20words%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Bfaggot%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bfallen%20woman%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bharlot%26quot%3B%20need%20to%20be%20done%20away%20with%20in%20court%20judgments.%20Instead%2C%20it%20said%2C%20judges%20should%20accurately%20describe%20the%20sexual%20orientation%20of%20the%20person%20concerned%20--%20homosexual%20or%20bisexual%2C%20use%20%26quot%3Bwoman%26quot%3B%20and%20avoid%20words%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Bfallen%20woman%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bharlot%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%220hvleboo%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F0hvleboo_supreme-court_625x300_16_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESource%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20website%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20words%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Bdutiful%20wife%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bobedient%20wife%26quot%3B%20should%20be%20avoided%2C%20the%20handbook%20stated.%20The%20use%20of%20words%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Bravished%26quot%3B%20in%20cases%20of%20sexual%20assault%20or%20rape%20was%20also%20red-flagged%20in%20the%20handbook.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20handbook%20also%20busted%20several%20stereotypes%20attached%20to%20women%2C%20such%20as%20women%20being%20overly%20emotional%20and%20indecisive%2C%20unmarried%20women%20being%20incapable%20of%20taking%20decisions%20and%20all%20women%20wanting%20to%20have%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20glossary%20aims%20to%20help%20the%20Indian%20judiciary%20identify%20and%20mitigate%20the%20use%20of%20stereotypes%20and%20stereotype-enforcing%20language%20against%20women%20in%20their%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20states%20the%20handbook%2C%20which%20has%20now%20been%20uploaded%20on%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692176160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-whore-faggot-slut-supreme-courts-handbook-red-flags-gender-bias-4302063%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prostitute%2C%20hooker%2C%20whore%2C%20keep%2C%20mistress%2C%20slut%2C%20faggot%20--%20these%20are%20among%2040-odd%20words%20red-flagged%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20its%20latest%20handbook%20to%20sensitise%20judges%20against%20inadvertently%20furthering%20gender%20biases%20by%20using%20stereotypical%20words%20in%20court%20j%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-whore-faggot-slut-supreme-courts-handbook-red-flags-gender-bias-4302063%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-whore-faggot-slut-supreme-courts-handbook-red-flags-gender-bias-4302063%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-whore-faggot-slut-supreme-courts-handbook-red-flags-gender-bias-4302063%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20'Amit%20Shah's%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speech%20Has%20Made%20Things%20Worse%20in%20Manipur%2C%20Irresponsible%20Not%20to%20Remove%20Biren'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16142156%2FKT-16-August.00_57_01_06.Still001.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EHighly%20regarded%20human%20rights%20activists%20from%20Manipur%20and%20director%20of%20Human%20Rights%20Alert%20Babloo%20Loitongbam%20has%20said%20that%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20two-hour%20speech%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20last%20week%2C%20where%20Amit%20Shah%20explained%20the%20crisis%20in%20Manipur%20by%20citing%20the%20influx%20of%20Kuki%20refugees%20from%20Burma%2C%20has%20made%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%9Cworse%E2%80%9D.%20Loitongbam%20said%20this%20explanation%20is%20one-sided%20and%20at%20best%20a%20%E2%80%9Chalf-truth%E2%80%9D.%20After%20the%20home%20minister%20spoke%20on%20August%209%2C%20his%20speech%20has%20been%20vehemently%20refuted%20by%20all%20ten%20Kuki%20MLAs%2C%20the%20Kuki%20Inpi%20and%20the%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%20Forum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Loitongbam%20also%20said%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cirresponsible%E2%80%9D%20not%20to%20remove%20N.%20Biren%20Singh.%20With%20the%20entire%20Kuki%20population%20having%20lost%20faith%20in%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20and%20with%2015%20out%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%2032%20MLAs%20taking%20the%20same%20position%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstubborn%E2%80%9D%20insistence%20on%20retaining%20Biren%20Singh%20is%20prolonging%20if%20not%20exacerbating%20the%20problem.%20A%20new%20BJP%20chief%20minister%2C%20who%20no%20doubt%20will%20be%20Meitei%2C%20would%20provide%20an%20opportunity%20to%20start%20some%20sort%20of%20peace%20process%20and%20it%20would%20also%20appease%20the%20Kuki%20community%2C%20who%20are%2016%25%20of%20the%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FkK4afNQe8fg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELoitongbam%20is%20a%20Meitei%20who%20has%20faced%20violent%20threats%20from%20Meitei%20organisations%20like%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20and%20Meitei%20Leepun%20because%20of%20the%20stand%20he%E2%80%99s%20taken%20on%20the%20crisis%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELoitongbam%20makes%20clear%20that%20the%20situation%20could%20have%20been%20nipped%20in%20the%20bud%20as%20early%20as%20May%203%20or%204%20if%20the%20chief%20minister%20had%20acted.%20He%20says%20it%20was%20negligence%20on%20the%20part%20of%20Biren%20Singh%20not%20to%20do%20so.%20When%20asked%20if%20this%20negligence%20was%20followed%20or%20succeeded%20by%20a%20measure%20of%20complicity%20in%20wanting%20the%20crisis%20to%20continue%2C%20Loitongbam%20said%20that%20it%20would%20be%20a%20problem%20back%20home%20if%20he%20were%20to%20agree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmongst%20the%20issues%20that%20are%20discussed%20in%20the%20interview%20is%20the%20Meitei%20demand%20to%20replace%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20the%20Kuki%20demand%20to%20restrain%20and%20stop%20Manipur%20police%20entering%20the%20hill%20areas%2C%20the%20army%20request%20for%20restraint%20on%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20who%20block%20roads%20and%20hold%20up%20army%20convoys%2C%20the%20Meitei%20perception%20of%20a%20land%20imbalance%20and%20their%20demand%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Kuki%20demand%20for%20separate%20administration%2C%20which%20they%20say%20means%20a%20separate%20state%20or%20union%20territory.%20There%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20substantial%20discussion%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20handling%20of%20the%20crisis%20and%20what%20his%20silence%20%E2%80%93%20now%20limited%20comments%20%E2%80%93%20suggest%20of%20his%20attitude%20to%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELoitongbam%20says%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20civil%20society%20organisations%20and%20individuals%20to%20come%20together%2C%20facilitated%20by%20the%20government%2C%20and%20throw%20up%20out%20of%20the%20box%20ideas%20and%20start%20discussing%20them.%20He%20says%20although%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20apparent%20to%20people%20outside%20Manipur%2C%20this%20process%20has%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692176145000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16142156%2FKT-16-August.00_57_01_06.Still001.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwatch-amit-shahs-lok-sabha-speech-has-made-things-worse-in-manipur-irresponsible-not-to-remove-biren%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Babloo%20Loitongbam%20says%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20civil%20society%20organisations%20and%20individuals%20to%20come%20together%2C%20facilitated%20by%20the%20government%2C%20and%20throw%20up%20out%20of%20the%20box%20ideas%20and%20start%20discussing%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwatch-amit-shahs-lok-sabha-speech-has-made-things-worse-in-manipur-irresponsible-not-to-remove-biren%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Women's%20World%20Cup%202023%3A%20'Football%20fever%20has%20taken%20over%20New%20Zealand'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A169