%20also%20under%20the%20scanner%20for%20the%20violence%20in%20Nuh.%20Manesar%2C%20who%20is%20wanted%20over%20his%20alleged%20role%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20two%20Muslim%20men%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20arrested.%20As%20he%20evades%20arrest%2C%20Manesar%20continues%20to%20post%20inflammatory%20material%20on%20social%20media.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBittu%20Bajrangi%20is%20accused%20of%20stoking%20communal%20tension%20ahead%20of%20a%20march%20organised%20by%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20in%20Haryana's%20Nuh%20by%20putting%20up%20inflammatory%20videos.%20He%20was%20also%20present%20during%20the%20yatra.%20Bittu%20Bajrangi%20was%20arrested%20earlier%20on%20August%204%2C%20and%20was%20out%20on%20bail.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAccording%20to%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%2C%20Bittu%20Bajrangi%20and%20his%20associates%20brandished%20weapons%20during%20the%20procession%20that%20was%20attacked%20by%20a%20mob.%20The%20weapons%20were%20seized%20by%20police%2C%20but%20Bajrangi%20and%20his%20aides%20allegedly%20attacked%20a%20police%20vehicle%20and%20snatched%20them%20back.%20The%20police%20officer%20said%20they%20also%20threatened%20cops.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20FIR%20against%20Bittu%20Bajrangi%20and%20at%20least%2015%20others%20accuses%20them%20of%20rioting%2C%20unlawful%20assembly%2C%20obstructing%20a%20public%20servant%20from%20discharging%20duty%2C%20armed%20robbery%20and%20criminal%20intimidation.%20They%20have%20also%20been%20charged%20under%20provisions%20of%20Arms%20Act.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692175380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Frl8uq6s8_bittu-bajrangi_625x300_16_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-violence-nuh-violence-bittu-bajrangi-monu-manesar-5-facts-on-bittu-bajrangi-cow-vigilante-arrested-in-haryana-violence-case-4301861%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bittu%20Bajrangi%2C%20head%20of%20a%20cow%20vigilante%20group%20in%