e.in%2Fauthor%2Fpulapre-balakrishnan%5C%22%3EPulapre%20Balakrishnan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20put%20in%20his%20papers%20in%20solidarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%2C%20issued%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20entire%20department%20and%20posted%20on%20X%20(Twitter)%20by%20Professor%20Ashwini%20Deshpande%20on%20August%2016%2C%20publicly%20makes%20two%20demands%3A%20that%20Das%20be%20immediately%20reinstated%2C%20and%20that%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20governing%20body%20promise%20to%20not%20use%20a%20committee%20%E2%80%9Cor%20any%20other%20structure%E2%80%9D%20to%20evaluate%20faculty%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20the%20official%20statement%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Economics%20at%20Ashoka.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frodrikdani%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40rodrikdani%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSonaldeDesai%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40SonaldeDesai%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FN_Kabeer%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40N_Kabeer%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftajmahalfoxtrot%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40tajmahalfoxtrot%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frbalakra%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40rbalakra%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIAFFE%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40IAFFE%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FNF4Kaq2C19%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FNF4Kaq2C19%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Ashwini_Deshpande%20(%40_ADeshpande)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F_ADeshpande%2Fstatus%2F1691674452713738331%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2016%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20August%201%20tweet%20distancing%20itself%20from%20Das%20was%20widely%20criticised%20by%20academics%20in%20India%20and%20abroad%2C%20the%20trigger%20for%20Das%E2%80%99%20resignation%20appears%20to%20be%20an%20attempt%20by%20its%20governing%20body%20to%20%E2%80%98investigate%E2%80%99%20his%20recent%20paper%20and%20%E2%80%93%20according%20to%20university%20sources%20%E2%80%93%20get%20him%20to%20alter%20his%20title%20and%20abstract%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20economics%20department%20statement%20says%20that%20%E2%80%9CProf.%20Das%20did%20not%20violate%20any%20accepted%20norm%20of%20academic%20practice%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20adds%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAcademic%20research%20is%20professionally%20evaluated%20through%20a%20process%20of%20peer%20review.%20The%20Governing%20Body%E2%80%99s%20interference%20in%20this%20process%20to%20investigate%20the%20merits%20of%20his%20recent%20study%20constitutes%20institutional%20harassment%2C%20curtails%20academic%20freedom%2C%20and%20forces%20scholars%20to%20operate%20in%20an%20environment%20of%20fear.%20We%20condemn%20this%20in%20the%20strongest%20terms%20and%20refuse%20as%20a%20collective%20to%20cooperate%20in%20any%20future%20attempt%20to%20evaluate%20the%20research%20of%20individual%20economics%20faculty%20members%20by%20the%20governing%20body.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20university%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ashoka.edu.in%2Froles%2Fleadership-team%2F%3Ffilterby%3D320%5C%22%3Egoverning%20body%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20several%20of%20its%20promoters%20as%20members%2C%20amongst%20whom%20the%20two%20most%20prominent%20are%20Pramath%20Raj%20Sinha%20and%20Ashish%20Dhawan.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20them%2C%20and%20to%20the%20vice%20chancellor%20for%20a%20response%20to%20the%20economics%20department%E2%80%99s%20statement%20and%20this%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20as%20and%20when%20they%20reply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Coffer%20of%20resignation%20by%20our%20colleague%20Prof.%20Sabyasachi%20Das%20and%20its%20hasty%20acceptance%20by%20the%20university%20has%20deeply%20ruptured%20the%20faith%20that%20we%20in%20the%20faculty%20of%20the%20department%20of%20economics%2C%20our%20colleagues%2C%20our%20students%2C%20and%20well-wishers%20of%20Ashoka%20University%20everywhere%2C%20had%20reposed%20in%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20leadership%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20faculty%20set%20a%20deadline%20of%20August%2023%20to%20address%20its%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnless%20these%20questions%20regarding%20basic%20academic%20freedoms%20are%20resolved%20before%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Monsoon%202023%20semester%2C%20faculty%20members%20of%20the%20department%20will%20find%20themselves%20unable%20to%20carry%20forward%20their%20teaching%20obligations%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20critical%20enquiry%20and%20the%20fearless%20pursuit%20of%20truth%20that%20characterise%20our%20classrooms.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20English%20and%20creative%20writing%20departments%20of%20Ashoka%20University%20have%20also%20released%20a%20statement%20in%20solidarity%20with%20the%20Economics%20Department%2C%20stipulating%20the%20same%20demands.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20hope%2C%20too%2C%20that%20Ashoka%E2%80%99s%20official%20social%20media%20handles%20will%20cease%20putting%20out%20statements%20discrediting%20academic%20research%20by%20its%20faculty%20members%20in%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20write.%20A%20failure%20to%20meet%20these%20demands%20would%20result%20in%20the%20two%20departments%20joining%20the%20economics%20department%20in%20its%20boycott%20of%20classes%20during%20the%20monsoon%202023%20semester.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20faculty%20members%20raise%20concerns%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20its%20website%2C%20%E2%80%9CAshoka%20University%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20leading%20Liberal%20Arts%20and%20Sciences%20University%20providing%20a%20distinctive%20interdisciplinary%20liberal%20education%20at%20par%20with%20the%20best%20universities%20in%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%20But%20recent%20events%20have%20cast%20a%20shadow%20over%20these%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20separate%20statement%20by%2082%20faculty%20members%2C%20drafted%20before%20Das%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20had%20been%20accepted%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFree%20thought%20within%20universities%20in%20India%20is%20in%20crisis%20today%2C%20largely%20because%20of%20the%20near-absolute%20intolerance%20of%20critique%E2%80%A6.%20To%20stifle%20critique%20is%20to%20poison%20the%20life-blood%20of%20pedagogy%3B%20consequently%2C%20it%20is%20to%20damage%20whatever%20future%20our%20students%20might%20have%20as%20serious%20thinkers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%2C%20signed%20by%20Amit%20Chaudhuri%2C%20Rita%20Kothari%2C%20Ratul%20Lahkar%2C%20Deepak%20Mehta%2C%20Nayanjot%20Lahiri%2C%20Saikat%20Majumdar%2C%20S.M.%20Bhattacharjee%2C%20Aparna%20Vaidik%2C%20Rajendra%20Bhatia%2C%20Mukul%20Sharma%2C%20Madhavi%20Menon%2C%20Bikram%20Phookan%2C%20Pulapre%20Balakrishnan%20and%2069%20others%2C%20says%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRecent%20events%20around%20a%20paper%20published%20by%20Professor%20Sabyasachi%20Das%20are%20a%20reminder%20that%20the%20crisis%20is%20an%20ongoing%20and%20deep%20one%2C%20with%20implications%20for%20every%20academic%20working%20at%20Ashoka%20University%20and%2C%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20in%20India%E2%80%A6%20It%20is%20not%20a%20crisis%20that%20will%20go%20away%20by%20wishing%20that%20papers%20like%20Professor%20Das%E2%80%99%20will%20not%20be%20written%20in%20the%20future%2C%20because%20that%20is%20not%20a%20realistic%20possibility%20in%20a%20working%20institution.%20It%20will%20not%20be%20solved%20by%20apologies%20and%20resignations.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20addressed%20with%20academic%20freedom%20constituting%20the%20core%20of%20our%20position%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20crisis.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20notes%20that%20though%20the%20university%20had%20drafted%20and%20adopted%20a%20document%20for%20academic%20freedom%20in%202021%2C%20it%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9Cbewildering%20to%20witness%20events%20unfold%20in%20the%20last%20two%20weeks%20that%20are%20directly%20related%20to%20academic%20freedom%20in%20a%20way%20that%20makes%20no%20reference%20to%20this%20document%20and%20behaves%2C%20to%20all%20purposes%2C%20as%20if%20it%20does%20not%20exist%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20signatories%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Call%20responses%20to%20the%20matter%20of%20what%20may%20or%20may%20not%20be%20admissible%20in%20research%20and%20academic%20practice%20at%20Ashoka%20University%E2%80%9D%20should%20be%20handled%20as%20per%20the%20guidelines%20set%20out%20in%20that%20document%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhich%2C%20rather%20than%20any%20tweet%20or%20individual%20opinion%2C%20expresses%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20position%20on%20this%20all-important%20subject%E2%80%9D.%20They%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Committee%20for%20Academic%20Freedom%2C%20which%20the%20document%20had%20proposed%20be%20set%20up%20soon%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbe%20created%20immediately%E2%80%9D%20to%20bring%20%E2%80%9Cmuch-needed%20transparency%20and%20procedural%20fairness%20whenever%20such%20issues%20arise.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalakrishnan%20has%20since%20also%20resigned%20from%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Ashoka%20vice-chancellor%20Somak%20Raychaudhury%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20university%20%E2%80%9Caffords%20its%20faculty%20and%20students%20the%20most%20enabling%20environment%20for%20academic%20freedom%20at%20an%20institution%20of%20higher%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20this%20%E2%80%9Cacademic%20freedom%20also%20applied%20to%20Mr.%20Das%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20charge%20levelled%20by%20the%20economics%20department%20casts%20doubts%20on%20this%20assurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%2C%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20stand%20on%20Das%20has%20drawn%20criticism%20from%20students%20and%20academics%2C%20especially%20given%20the%20track%20record%20of%20how%20it%20had%20handled%20its%20reputed%20vice%20chancellor%20Pratap%20Bhanu%20Mehta%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fpratap-bhanu-mehta-resigns-as-professor-at-ashoka-university%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%252520a%252520letter%252520to%252520students%2CVC%252520rather%252520than%252520stop%252520writing.%5C%22%3Ewhen%20he%20was%20both%20nudged%20and%20persuaded%20to%20resign%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20March%202021%20due%20to%20his%20media%20writings%20on%20the%20politics%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20critic%20called%20Ashoka%E2%80%99s%20comment%20on%20Das%E2%80%99%20paper%20an%20example%20of%C2%A0%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2Fi%2F135712802%2Fashoka-universitys-response-to-its-own-faculty-is-democratic-backsliding-in-academia%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98democratic%20backsliding%20in%20academia%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fashoka-university-resignations-kashmir%5C%22%3Eallegations%20had%20been%20levelled%20by%20the%20faculty%20council%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20founders%20had%20asked%20two%20members%20of%20the%20non-teaching%20staff%20%E2%80%93%20deputy%20manager%20of%20academic%20affairs%20Saurav%20Goswami%20and%20programme%20manager%20of%20academic%20affairs%20Adil%20Mushtaq%20Shah%20%E2%80%93%20and%20one%20faculty%20member%2C%20Rajendran%20Narayanan%2C%20to%20resign%20in%202016%2C%20over%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20had%20signed%20a%20petition%20against%20violence%20in%20Kashmir%20after%20Burhan%20Wani%E2%80%99s%20death%20and%20demanded%20a%20plebiscite%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692174136000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F25160938%2Fashoka.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fecon-dept-says-ashoka-governing-body-interferen