011%20by%20sports%20department%20director%20Yashendra%20Singh%2C%20read%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20services%20of%20the%20Junior%20Athletic%20Coach%2C%20(posted%20in%20the%20office%20of)%20district%20sports%20officer%2C%20Panchkula%20are%20placed%20under%20suspension%20with%20immediate%20effect%20without%20prejudice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20did%20not%20list%20any%20reason%20for%20her%20suspension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coach%20had%20filed%20an%20FIR%20against%20Singh%20in%20December%202022%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20charges%20of%20stalking%2C%20illegal%20confinement%2C%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20criminal%20intimidation%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fchandigarh%2Fwoman-coach-sexual-harassment-allegations-haryana-minister-sandeep-singh-8894580%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20I%20have%20been%20suspended.%20Pressure%20is%20being%20mounted%20on%20me%20to%20hammer%20out%20a%20compromise%20(to%20withdraw%20the%20case).%20I%20have%20not%20been%20intimated%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20my%20suspension.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20why%20they%20have%20taken%20this%20step.%20This%20is%20yet%20another%20way%20for%20the%20government%20to%20pressurise%20me%2C%20but%20I%20am%20not%20going%20to%20yield%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20coach%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20handed%20the%20suspension%20order%20at%20her%20residence%20on%20Monday%20evening%20despite%20attending%20office%20that%20day%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20order%2C%20she%20will%20be%20entitled%20to%20subsistence%20allowance%20as%20admissible%20under%20Rule%2083%20of%20Haryana%20Civil%20Services%20(general)%20Rules%2C%202016%20and%20her%20post%20during%20the%20suspension%20period%20will%20remain%20the%20office%20of%20district%20sports%20officer%2C%20Panchkula%20where%20she