AM-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F16115131%2FScreenshot-2023-08-16-at-11.51.05-AM-1024x682.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668285%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22799%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPOSTSCRIPT%20%2F%20SNAPSHOTS%20FROM%20MANIPUR%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnSyeda%20Hameed%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20sense%20I%20am%20in%20a%20foreign%20country.%20The%20word%20LoC%20is%20bandied%20around.%20Barricades%20are%20visible%20everywhere.%20It%20is%20a%20war%20zone.%20It%E2%80%99s%20as%20if%20two%20countries%20are%20struggling%20to%20be%20born.%20Meiteis%20and%20Kukis%2C%20in%20full%20battle%20gear%2C%20are%20ranged%20on%20either%20side.%20AK%2047%2C%20bombs%2C%20hand%20grenades.%20Sights%20and%20sounds%20which%20send%20a%20chill%20body%20signal.%20I%20am%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20small%20delegation%20of%204%20women.%203%20from%20the%20North%20East%20and%20me.%20I%2C%20Kashmir%20born%2C%20partition%20torn%2C%20stand%20on%20the%20debris%20of%20a%20land%20that%20is%20rightly%20known%20as%20the%20most%20precious%20jewel%20of%20India.%20I%20stand%20here%20because%20since%20the%20last%2020%20years%20when%20Kangla%20Fort%20was%20handed%20to%20people%2C%20I%20have%20identified%20with%20Manipur.%20Today%20we%20are%20in%20mourning.%20Wamiq%20Jaunpuri%20wrote%20these%20lines%20%E2%80%98Who%20will%20answer%3F%E2%80%99%20when%20Gandhiji%20was%20assassinated.%20Today%20they%20resonate%20with%20Manipur%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYe%20kaun%20qatl%20ho%20gaya%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EYe%20kaun%20dil%20ka%20raaz%20sabse%20kehte%20kehte%20so%20gaya%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EJawab%20iska%20kaun%20de%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EKe%20khud%20hamare%20haath%20iss%20lahu%20mein%20hain%20rangey%20huey%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20has%20been%20killed%3F%3Cbr%3E%5CnWho%20has%20been%20put%20to%20sleep%20while%20pouring%20out%20his%20heart%3F%20Who%20will%20answer%3F%3Cbr%3E%5CnWe%3F%20But%20our%20hands%20are%20dyed%20in%20the%20same%20blood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20my%20thoughts%20which%20I%20need%20to%20express%20while%20they%20rage%20within%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScene%20One%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImages%20rise%20on%20the%20mind.%20We%20are%20on%20our%20way%20to%20Churachandpur.%20We%20reach%20Kwatka%20Bazar%2C%20a%20Pangal-Muslim%20village.%20It%20is%20raining.%20Hundreds%20of%20women%20are%20sitting%20in%20partly%20covered%20shelters%20along%20the%20road%20which%20leads%20to%20the%20LoC%20dividing%20Bishnupur%20from%20Churachandpur.%20Hundreds%20of%20men%20swarm%20around%2C%20many%20with%20guns.%203%20Meiteis%2C%20father-son%20and%20their%20friend%20have%20been%20butchered%20then%20shot%20at%203%20AM.%20Their%20bodies%20are%20still%20lying%20there.%E2%80%98%20Pay%20your%20respects%E2%80%99%20we%20are%20asked.%20I%20cover%20my%20head%20with%20my%20namaaz%20scarf.%20We%20walk%20towards%20the%20women.%20In%20their%20midst%20is%20the%20young%20wife%20of%20the%20victim.%20My%20colleagues%20bend%20down%20to%20hug%20her%20trembling%20form%20and%20let%20their%20tears%20mingle%20with%20hers.%20We%20hear%20shots%2C%20cross%20firing%20very%20close%3B%20my%20heart%20lurches.%20This%20is%20the%20end%20but%20we%20cannot%20move.%20I%20have%20just%20finished%20mourning%20for%20the%20martyrs%20of%20Karbala%3B%20Bishnupur%20and%20Churachandpur%20are%20also%20Karbala.%20We%20get%20up%20and%20move%20to%20the%20car%3B%20a%20man%20appears%20at%20the%20window.%20%E2%80%98He%20is%20Nobo%20Volcano%2C%20beloved%20Manipuri%20singer.%E2%80%99%20someone%20says.%20In%20a%20loud%20voice%20he%20shouts%20into%20the%20cameras%20being%20held%20before%20his%20face.%20%E2%80%98%20Modi!%20We%20voted%20you%20in%3B%20in%20the%20centre%20and%20state.%20And%20you%3F%20You%20have%20betrayed%20us.%20You%20have%20let%20us%20butcher%20each%20other%2C%20rape%20and%20kill%20our%20daughters%20while%20you%20and%20your%20Manipur%20colleague%20are%20watching%20from%20your%20far%20off%20high%20perches.%E2%80%99%3Cbr%3E%5CnFour%20of%20us%20plus%20two%20of%20the%20brightest%20and%20kindest%20women%20from%20this%20state%20who%20have%20accompanied%20us%2C%20sit%20in%20stunned%20silence%20while%20word%20comes%20from%20the%20border%20that%20any%20further%20movement%20is%20fraught%20with%20danger.%20We%20turn%20back.%20We%20were%20just%2015%20kms%20from%20the%20Line%20of%20Control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScene%20Two%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20it%20were%20the%20Kuki%20we%20saw%20as%20we%20entered%20district%20Tengnopal%20from%20Imphal.%20The%20last%20post%2C%20Moreh%20is%2030%20kms%20from%20Burma%20border.%20Moreh%20is%20where%20long%20ago%20we%20went%20for%20shopping%20for%20gadgets%20smuggled%20from%20Burma.%20From%20the%20car%20window%2C%20while%20it%20poured%20heavily%2C%20we%20watched%20the%20large%20sign%20Separate%20Administration.%20In%20the%20downpour%20we%20saw%20more%20than%20a%20thousand%20women%20and%20girls%20sitting%20in%20the%20open%20in%20defiance%20of%20both%20the%20elements%20and%20the%20central%20and%20state%20governments.%20Drenched%20but%20not%20subdued.%20Two%20women%2C%20equally%20strong%2C%20balanced%20and%20sensitive%20steered%20the%20meeting%20which%20was%20held%20in%20a%20shed%2C%20slightly%20set%20back%20from%20the%20main%20road%20leading%20to%20Moreh.%20Kuki%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Union%20for%20Human%20Rights%20Voices%20rose%20around%20us%3B%20%E2%80%98We%20are%20betrayed%20so%20brutally%3B%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20believe%20in%20uniforms%2C%20in%20fake%20id-cards.%20Militias%20in%20army%20uniforms%20raze%20our%20homes%20and%20kill%20us%3B%20Arambai%20Tengot%20and%20Meitei%20Leipum.%20We%20demand%20separate%20administration%20for%20the%20Kuki-%20Zo%20Tribal%20People.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20of%20lines%20from%20Sahir%20Ludhianvi%20as%20the%20first%20glimmer%20of%20light%20in%20this%20dark%20tunnel%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELaakh%20baithe%