erpent-named-after-harrison-ford-12940904%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwhyd-it-have-to-be-snakes-new-species-of-serpent-named-after-harrison-ford-12940904%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwhyd-it-have-to-be-snakes-new-species-of-serpent-named-after-harrison-ford-12940904%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Breakthrough%20at%20India-China%20Military%20Talks%2C%20Joint%20Statement%20Says%20Countries%20Will%20Keep%20Border%20Peace%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F07085318%2FChina-india.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Despite%20indicating%20a%20lack%20of%20significant%20progress%2C%20India%20and%20China%20issued%20a%20joint%20press%20release%20a%20day%20after%20the%20high-level%20military%20talks%20ended%2C%20with%20a%20declaration%20to%20maintain%20tranquility%20at%20the%20borders%20and%20resolve%20remaining%20issues%20expeditiously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2019th%20round%20of%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20corps%20commander-level%20meeting%20took%20place%20in%20Chushul-Moldo%20meeting%20point%20on%20August%2013-14.%20The%20meeting%20ended%20at%20around%205%3A30%20pm%20on%20Monday%2C%20but%20it%20took%20more%20than%2024%20hours%20for%20the%20two%20sides%20to%20release%20a%20joint%20press%20release.%20There%20had%20been%20no%20joint%20statement%20issued%20after%20the%20last%20round%20of%20military%20talks%20held%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20is%20significant%20as%20it%20takes%20place%20less%20than%20a%20month%20before%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20is%20scheduled%20to%20travel%20to%20Delhi%20for%20the%20annual%20G20%20leaders%E2%80%99%20summit.%20Ahead%20of%20that%2C%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20meet%20Xi%20for%20the%20BRICS%20summit%20next%20week%20in%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20press%20release%20claimed%20that%20the%20two%20sides%20had%20a%20%E2%80%9Chad%20a%20positive%2C%20constructive%20and%20in-depth%20discussion%20on%20the%20resolution%20of%20the%20remaining%20issues%20along%20the%20LAC%20in%20the%20Western%20Sector%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20it%20said%20there%20was%20an%20exchange%20of%20views%20in%20an%20%E2%80%9Copen%20and%20forward-looking%20manner%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cin%20line%20with%20the%20guidance%20provided%20by%20the%20leadership%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20Asian%20neighbours%20%E2%80%9Cagreed%20to%20resolve%20the%20remaining%20issues%20in%20an%20expeditious%20manner%20and%20maintain%20the%20momentum%20of%20dialogue%20and%20negotiations%20through%20military%20and%20diplomatic%20channels%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20this%2C%20India%20and%20China%20reiterated%20that%20that%20while%20the%20issues%20were%20being%20resolved%2C%20they%20will%20%E2%80%9Cmaintain%20the%20peace%20and%20tranquility%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20the%20border%20areas%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20sides%20have%20been%20engaged%20in%20a%20stand-off%20at%20Eastern%20Ladakh%20since%20May%202020%2C%20which%20led%20to%20a%20major%20hand-to-hand%20clash%20at%20Galwan%20valley%20that%20left%2024%20soldiers%20dead.%20Since%20then%20there%20have%20been%20multiple%20rounds%20of%20talks%20which%20led%20to%20disengagement%20at%20around%20four%20friction%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20strategic%20areas%20of%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok%20have%20stalemated%20the%20talks.%20China%20has%20been%20urging%20India%20to%20move%20beyond%20the%20stand-off%20and%20discuss%20these%20two%20remaining%20issues%20as%20part%20of%20the%20larger%20boundary%20question.%20However%2C%20India%20has%20so%20far%20insisted%20that%20the%20stand-off%20cannot%20be%20resolved%20till%20the%20armies%20disengage%20at%20these%20two%20points%20and%20the%20traditional%20patrolling%20points%20in%20the%20area%20are%20restored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20joint%20statement%2C%20former%20Indian%20ambassador%20to%20China%20Ashok%20Kantha%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAny%20resolution%20must%20involve%20restoration%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20pre-May%202020%20patrolling%20rights%20at%20all%20%E2%80%98friction%20points%E2%80%99%20and%20not%20merely%20creation%20of%20%E2%80%98buffer%20zones%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIndia-China%20Corps%20Commanders%E2%80%99%20Meeting%20on%20border%20standoff%20concludes%20without%20breakthrough%20on%20disengagement%20in%20Dapsang%20and%20Demchok.%20Any%20resolution%20must%20involve%20restoration%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20pre-May%202020%20patrolling%20rights%20at%20all%20%E2%80%98friction%20points%E2%80%99%20and%20not%20merely%20creation%20of%20%E2%80%98buffer%20zones%E2%80%99.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FUnnvhPGc5o%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FUnnvhPGc5o%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20ashokkantha%20(%40ashokkkantha)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fashokkkantha%2Fstatus%2F1691471810653736960%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2015%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692155045000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F07085318%2FChina-india.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fno-breakthrough-at-india-china-military-talks-joint-statement-says-countries-will-keep-border-peace%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2019th%20round%20of%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20corps%20commander-level%20meeting%20took%20place%20in%20Chushul-Moldo%20meeting%20point%20on%20August%2013-14.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fno-breakthrough-at-india-china-military-talks-joint-statement-says-countries-will-k