0and%20shops%20owned%20by%20Muslims%20were%20razed%20to%20the%20ground.%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20lane%2C%20where%20only%20Hindus%20live%2C%20remains%20untouched%20by%20the%20demolitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20lived%20among%20Muslims%20in%20harmony%20all%20our%20lives%2C%20we%20have%20never%20faced%20any%20verbal%20insult%2C%20let%20alone%20harassment%20and%20violence.%20I%20feel%20bad%20that%20their%20homes%20are%20broken%2C%20that%20they%E2%80%99re%20scared%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Singh%2C%20a%20millets%20farmer.%20Twelve%20other%20Hindu%20families%20live%20in%20the%20same%20lane%20as%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15110842%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-15-at-10.57.45-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15110842%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-15-at-10.57.45-AM.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15110842%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-15-at-10.57.45-AM-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15110842%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-15-at-10.57.45-AM-1024x576.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668153%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIn%20Nalhar%2C%20Dharamveer%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20lane%20near%20the%20demolitions%20remains%20untouched.%20More%20than%2010%20Hindu%20families%20live%20here.%20Photo%3A%20Tarushi%20Aswani%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20says%20that%20there%20is%20such%20amity%20and%20brotherhood%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20in%20Nuh%20that%20beyond%20a%20point%2C%20religion%20stops%20interfering%20in%20their%20daily%20lives.%20Whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20business%20or%20banter%20about%20development%2C%20Singh%20explains%20that%20Nuh%20has%20never%20been%20a%20fertile%20ground%20for%20anti-Muslim%20hate.%20Though%20Nuh%20is%20Muslim-dominated%2C%20Hindus%20in%20the%20district%20said%20that%20the%20community%20has%20never%20asserted%20its%20dominance%20over%20the%20local%20minorities%2C%20which%20also%20includes%20the%20Sikh%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20half-done%20Azimiya%20Masjid%2C%20which%20sits%20just%20opposite%20the%20college%2C%20is%20surrounded%20by%20hills%20of%20debris.%20Maulana%20Khalid%2C%20the%20imam%20of%20the%20mosque%2C%20is%20worried%20about%20the%20electricity%20pole%20which%20was%20mistakenly%20damaged%20during%20the%20demolition%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20mosque%20was%20spared%2C%20all%20surrounding%20shacks%20and%20shanties%20near%20it%20were%20toppled.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20an%20area%20where%20we%20have%20always%20respected%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20religions.%20When%20the%20%5BShobha%5D%20Yatra%20reached%20the%20mosque%2C%20we%20saw%20Hindus%20chanting%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shree%20Ram%E2%80%99%20and%20waving%20swords%20and%20sticks.%20We%20offered%20them%20water%20respectfully%2C%20as%20they%20were%20doing%20their%20religious%20duty%2C%E2%80%9D%20Khalid%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhalid%20also%20says%20that%20many%20non-Muslim%20patients%20from%20the%20hospital%20would%20come%20this%20masjid%20to%20bathe%20and%20get%20water%20when%20there%20was%20a%20shortage%20at%20the%20hospital.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20nothing%20called%20Hindu-Muslim%20problems%20here%2C%20we%20have%20lived%20in%20peace%20and%20still%20want%20to%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20loss%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAas%20Mohammed%2C%20a%20security%20guard%20at%20the%20nearby%20medical%20college%2C%20recently%20lost%20a%20part%20of%20his%20home%20to%20the%20Haryana%20government%E2%80%99s%20demolition%20drive%20that%20closely%20followed%20the%20communal%20violen