ions%20for%20me.%20That%20makes%20no%20sense%20to%20me.%20We%20are%20so%20stuck%20up%20with%20this%20%5Boutdated%20notions%20of%20traditionality%5D.%20There%20is%20a%20reason%20why%20I%E2%80%99m%20so%20proactively%20talking%20about%20it%20and%20so%20entrenched%20in%20that%20public%20discourse%20because%20nobody%20did%20that%20for%20us.%20So%2C%20now%20we%20have%20to%20do%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-06-1691803263.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Performer%20from%20India%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-06-1691803263.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-06-1691803263-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-06-1691803263-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-06-1691803263-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-06-1691803263-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FNavin-Noronha-06-1691803263-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327144%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EYou%20can%20catch%20Navin%20Noronha%E2%80%99s%20shows%20in%20these%20cities%20in%20August%202023.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERisque%20comedy%2C%20hope%20for%20the%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20creating%20a%20haven%20for%20queer%20people%20who%20can%20just%20laugh%20and%20be%20themselves%2C%20Navin%20has%20built%20a%20special%20environment.%20%E2%80%9CQueer%20people%20are%20bringing%20other%20queer%20people%20to%20my%20shows.%20My%20special%20sold%20out%20primarily%20through%20word%20of%20mouth%20because%20half%20the%20people%20at%20the%20show%20were%20queer.%20Apart%20from%20my%20solo%20shows%2C%20when%20we%20do%20the%20line-up%20shows%2C%20more%20people%20show%20up%20because%20of%20the%20diversity%20in%20the%20lineup%20and%20the%20other%20comics%20bring%20in%20their%20fanbase%20too.%20We%20have%20comics%20from%20across%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20spectrum%2C%20and%20the%20scene%20is%20developing%20for%20the%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20he%20also%20sees%20hope%20in%20the%20younger%20generation.%20%E2%80%9CUnlike%20our%20generation%20(millennials)%2C%20Gen%20Zs%20have%20their%20photo%2C%20biodata%2C%20Instagram%20link%2C%20Spotify%20link%20and%20sometimes%20even%20a%20link%20to%20their%20HIV%20test%20results%20on%20their%20social%20media%20handles.%20I%20envy%20them.%20What%20I%20love%20is%20that%20they%20have%20access.%20Growing%20up%2C%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20YouTube%2C%20TikTok%20or%20Instagram%2C%20i.e.%20an%20outlet%20%5Bwhere%20we%20could%20express%20our%20queer%20identities%5D.%20For%20me%2C%20comedy%20was%20an%20outlet.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20them%20are%20so%20fierce%20with%20makeup.%20I%20never%20had%20the%20courage%20to%20wear%20makeup%20in%20my%20younger%20days.%20Today%2C%20you%20have%20young%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F289628%2Fbengaluru-drag-artist-queen-beyonce-pride-month%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrag%20queens%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20drag%20kings%20and%20gender%20benders%20putting%20themselves%20out%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHaving%20said%20that%2C%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20are%20still%20getting%20kicked%20out%20of%20their%20houses%20for%20being%20gay%20and%20they%E2%80%99re%20still%20facing%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20same%20issues%20we%20faced.%20But%20what%20the%20queer%20community%20has%20now%20is%20a%20more%20prominent%20public%20voice%20and%20a%20face%20with%20important%20changes%20in%20the%20law%20to%20protect%20us.%20Also%2C%20there%20are%20so%20many%20nonprofits%20working%20behind%20the%20scenes%20to%20assist%20queer%20people%20in%20times%20of%20trouble.%20My%20job%20is%20nothing%20in%20comparison%20to%20all%20the%20people%20on%20the%20ground%20like%20the%20lawyers%20and%20activists%20who%20are%20filing%20these%20appeals%20and%20public%20interest%20litigations%20(PILs)%20in%20these%20landmark%20cases%20for%20queer%20rights.%20My%20job%20has%20been%20more%20on%20the%20sidelines%20like%20a%20jester%20saying%20%E2%80%98hey%20look%20at%20us%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98we%20exist%20too%E2%80%99.%20I%E2%80%99m%20hopeful%20for%20the%20future%20because%20every%20generation%20moving%20forward%20is%20gradually%20breaking%20down%20barriers%20for%20queer%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FS42H75GuLv4%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26rel%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D0%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26color%3Dred%26controls%3D1%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu%3B%20Images%20and%20Reels%20courtesy%20Navin%20Noronha%2F%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nof