es%20funds%20from%20the%20district%20administration.%20Himanshu%20says%20the%20activities%20at%20the%20child%20care%20homes%20are%20supervised%20regularly.%20%E2%80%9CI%20personally%20visit%20at%20least%20one%20home%20every%20week.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20challenges%20to%20run%20the%20campaign%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CUsually%20it%20takes%205-15%20days%20or%20more%20to%20reunite%20children%20with%20their%20families.%20But%20not%20all%20kids%20are%20the%20same.%20Some%20are%20intellectually%20disabled%20and%20it%20takes%20time%20to%20identify%20their%20homes%20as%20they%20are%20not%20able%20to%20communicate%20effectively.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Saurabh%20Maurya%2C%20who%20accompanies%20children%20to%20their%20homes%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20case%20of%20Shoaib%2C%20we%20had%20to%20use%20his%20biometrics%20to%20get%20his%20Aadhaar%20card%2C%20and%20address%20details%2C%20because%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20communicate%20about%20his%20home%20and%20parents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20big%20challenge%20to%20increase%20and%20better%20facilities%20at%20shelter%20homes.%20Also%2C%20coordination%20of%20the%20counterpart%20districts%20also%20matters.%20If%20the%20police%20stations%20there%20are%20not%20active%2C%20we%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20track%20their%20locations.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20one-time%20process.%20We%20have%20to%20be%20continuous%20in%20spearheading%20the%20campaign%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Himanshu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20feels%20that%20this%20work%20is%20also%20part%20of%20his%20duty.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20are%20unable%20to%20reunite%20these%20children%20with%20their%20families%2C%20then%20I%20do%20not%20think%20we%20are%20doing%20a%20good%20job.%20What%20we%20do%20is%20just%20part%20of%20my%20legal%20responsibilities.%20There%20have%20been%20moments%20when%20we%20see%20families%20crying%20with%20happin