ity-alumni-adopt-villages%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Osmania%20General%20Hospital%20(OGH)%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecampus%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20heritage%20block.%20In%20its%20place%2C%20the%20government%20plans%20to%20build%20a%20new%201800-bed%20facility.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20currently%20several%20public%20interest%20litigations%20(PIL)%20in%20the%20High%20Court%20that%20seek%20to%20preserve%20the%20heritage%20block.%C2%A0%20For%20instance%2C%20one%20filed%20by%20social%20activist%20Lubna%20Sarwath%20calls%20the%20demolition%20unconstitutional%20which%20will%20%E2%80%9Churt%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20identity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20State%20cannot%20afford%20the%20luxury%20of%20forgetting%20that%20the%20destruction%20of%20heritage%20buildings%20will%20rob%20its%20people%20of%20the%20essence%20of%20their%20identity%2C%20and%20will%20deprive%20the%20city%20of%20its%20sense%20of%20uniqueness.%20While%20it%20is%20important%20to%20plan%20for%20the%20future%2C%20it%20is%20equally%20important%20to%20protect%2C%20to%20preserve%20and%20to%20promote%20the%20past%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sarwath%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20want%20to%20preserve%20the%20heritage%20building%2C%20and%20want%20the%20new%20hospital%20to%20either%20be%20built%20around%20it%2C%20or%20at%20another%20location.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20take%20a%20look%20at%20what%20makes%20this%20hospital%20so%20iconic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHyderabad%E2%80%99s%20medical%20breakthroughs%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20724px)%20100vw%2C%20724px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fafzal-gunj-1691745063.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22724%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Afzal%20Gunj%20hospital%20was%20ravaged%20by%20the%20Musi%20floods%20in%201908%5C%22%20srcset%