20form.%20You%20can%20volunteer%20here%20as%20we%20are%20always%20short%20of%20hands%2C%20or%20you%20can%20also%20donate%20money%2C%20food%2C%20or%20medicines%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20regularly%20shares%20updates%20on%20the%20animals%E2%80%99%20health%20and%20well-being%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Sai%20is%20planning%20to%20build%20a%20quarantine%20centre%20in%20the%20sanctuary%20for%20animals%20with%20contagious%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20further%20his%20cause%2C%20you%20can%20reach%20Sai%20at%2089393%2020846.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691645042000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai-1-1691587222.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D326836%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sai%20Vignesh%20(22)%20started%20helping%20animals%20at%20a%20very%20young%20age%2C%20thanks%20to%20his%20parents%20and%20grandfather.%20Later%2C%20he%20started%20Almighty%20Animal%20Care%20Trust%20in%20Tiruvallur%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20provide%20a%20safe%20haven%20for%20animals.%20Currently%2C%20over%20250%20animals%20reside%20in%20his%20sanctuary.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A43%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326836%2Fsai-vignesh-rescuer-activist-started-almighty-animal-care-trust-chennai%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Better%20India%20Among%20Top%204%20Finalists%20for%20Prestigious%20Social%20Entrepreneur%20of%20the%20Year%20Award%2C%202023%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Anuradha%20Kedia%20and%20Dhimant%20Parekh%20co-founded%20The%20Better%20India%20in%202009%2C%20it%20was%20with%20a%20simple%20aim%20%E2%80%94%20to%20show%20an%20underreported%20and%20underrepresented%20faction%20of%20news%2C%20one%20that%20co