akes%20so%20far%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fvedhapriya-1691583306.jpeg%20588w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fvedhapriya-1691583306-170x300.jpeg%20170w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fvedhapriya-1691583306-500x884.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fvedhapriya-1691583306-150x265.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326808%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221040%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVedhapriya%20has%20rescued%20over%206%2C000%20snakes%20so%20far.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20remembers%20her%20first%20rescue%20like%20it%20was%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20snake%20in%20the%20area%20where%20she%20lived.%20%E2%80%9CA%20group%20of%20people%20had%20gathered%20with%20sticks%20in%20their%20hands.%20We%20used%20to%20call%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F12062%2Fmeet-snake-man-of-india-vava-suresh-thiruvananthapuram%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforest%20department%3C%2Fa%3E%20whenever%20we%20spotted%20a%20snake.%20However%2C%20they%20were%20busy%20that%20day%20and%20would%20take%20at%20least%20an%20hour%20to%20come%20to%20the%20spot%20at%20Maduravoyal.%20So%2C%20to%20prevent%20the%20onlookers%20from%20beating%20the%20snake%2C%20I%20lifted%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20later%20that%20she%20realised%20that%20the%20snake%20was%20in%20fact%20a%20cobra!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fvedha2-1691583886.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vedhapriya%20with%20an%20elephant%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset