0veterinary%20worker%2C%20driver%20and%20handler%20in%20each%20unit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20treating%20the%20animal%20on%20the%20field%2C%20we%20involve%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20particular%20area.%20It%E2%80%99s%20only%20when%20the%20community%20gets%20involved%20that%20the%20animal%20stands%20a%20chance%20of%20living%20a%20better%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Aditi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20work%20is%20not%20over%20after%20treating%20the%20animal%20on%20day%20one.%20We%20follow%20up%20daily%20till%20the%20animal%20is%20better.%20We%20teach%20residents%20who%20are%20around%20the%20animals%20how%20to%20take%20care%20of%20them%2C%20how%20often%20they%20have%20to%20be%20given%20saline%2C%20how%20to%20apply%20the%20ointments%20for%20them%2C%20etc%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20says%20that%20they%20educate%20people%20wherever%20they%20go%20on%20what%20diet%20can%20be%20offered%20to%20cats%20and%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20people%20give%20cow%E2%80%99s%20milk%20to%20dogs%20and%20cats%2C%20which%20they%20shouldn%E2%80%99t.%20They%20are%20usually%20lactose%20intolerant.%20%5BWe%20tell%20them%20that%5D%20even%20rotis%20or%20any%20wheat%20and%20maida%20products%20should%20be%20avoided.%20It%E2%80%99s%20better%20to%20give%20khichdi.%20So%20we%20try%20our%20best%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20animal%20is%20cared%20for%20well.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20case%20of%20paralysis%2C%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20defecate%20themselves.%20We%20teach%20people%20how%20to%20help%20them%20do%20that.%20For%20tick%20and%20flea%20care%2C%20you%20can%20simply%20massage%20eucalyptus%20oil%20on%20the%20skin.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMypalclub%20focuses%20on%20low-income%20areas%20in%20Thane.%20%E2%80%9CLarge%20societies%20and%20people%20with%20resources%20know%20that%20they%20can%20take%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F273674%2Fwelfare-for-animals-in-goa-started-by-real-life-hero-atul-sarin%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanimal%20to%20a%20veterinarian%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20have%20the%20resources%20for%20the%20same.%20We%20work%20in%20places%20where%20they%20don%E2%80%99t.%20In%20certain%20cases%2C%20where%20people%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20the%20medicines%2C%20we%20pay%20for%20that.%20Where%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20means%2C%20we%20help%20them%20with%20pet%20food%20also.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%201%2C000%20animals%20a%20month%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmypalclub-min-1691406839.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Animals%20being%20treated%20on%20field%20by%20Mypalclub%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmypalclub-min-1691406839.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmypalclub-min-1691406839-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmypalclub-min-1691406839-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmypalclub-min-1691406839-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmypalclub-min-1691406839-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326475%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAnimals%20being%20treated%20on%20field%20by%20Mypalclub%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMypalclub%20has%20three%20vehicles%20and%20their%20units%20help%2045-50%20animals%20every%20day%2C%20as%20well%20as%20about%201%2C000%20animals%20a%20month%2C%20says%20Aditi%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20have%20helped%20over%2040%2C000%20an